1
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,240
Lady Immortal

2
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,119
Quite the trick.

3
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:00,479
Shuisheng

4
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,399
What?

5
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,719
It really is Shuisheng.

6
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:13,760
Listen up!

7
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,519
Search every single room.

8
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:16,680
Take them all away!

9
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:17,599
Yes, sir!

10
00:01:18,239 --> 00:01:19,040
This way.

11
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:40,760
Qiuying.

12
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,480
Qiuying!

13
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,560
What are you doing?

14
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,719
I'm not doing anything.

15
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,319
Just cleaning up after the fight.

16
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,159
Of course,

17
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:05,319
grabbing some foreign goods.

18
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:18,280
Don't move.

19
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:20,759
You know what?

20
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,199
These mandarin ducks

21
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,560
really suit you.

22
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,159
They're yours.

23
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,360
What are you looking at?

24
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,120
I'm telling you, Shuisheng,

25
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,879
look at you.

26
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,560
You went home to get married.

27
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,319
I was still

28
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,000
waiting to toast at your wedding.

29
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:49,199
I really never expected

30
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,680
you'd become a bandit up in the hills.

31
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:55,759
Don't you know?

32
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:58,840
What I hate most in life is bandits.

33
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,319
Tell me,

34
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,319
did I

35
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,599
not treat you well enough?

36
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,280
I'm talking to you!

37
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,719
What are you looking at?

38
00:03:12,599 --> 00:03:14,319
Brigade Commander treated you like a son.

39
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:15,639
And what did you do?

40
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,840
You bit the hand that fed you.

41
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,319
And colluded with the Communists.

42
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,199
Beat him!

43
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,120
Talk!

44
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,039
Where did your wife go?

45
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,759
I brought you into the army,

46
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,159
fed you well, took care of you,

47
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:41,360
and now you're after my wife?

48
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,639
You don't mess with a friend's wife.

49
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,319
Don't you know that?

50
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:45,919
You animal!

51
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,479
You dare curse me?

52
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,560
All right, all right.

53
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,800
Hey, Dongsheng,

54
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,719
do you actually want to beat him to death?

55
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,159
Shuisheng,

56
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,639
for the sake

57
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,520
of the friendship we once had,

58
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,520
I'll give you three days.

59
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,000
Confess everything.

60
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,399
Otherwise,

61
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,319
I won't go easy on you.

62
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:33,319
Brother,

63
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:34,600
hang in there.

64
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:38,800
Talk!

65
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,000
Are you gonna talk or not?

66
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:42,279
Talk!

67
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,639
Master!

68
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:06,560
Bad news!

69
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,120
What's the rush?

70
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:11,639
Have some tea.

71
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,199
Master, I'm in no mood for tea!

72
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:14,800
Shuisheng was caught by the Brigade Commander.

73
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,720
What do you mean, "oh"?

74
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,560
"Oh" means I already know.

75
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,600
How did you know?

76
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,519
I told Master.

77
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:27,920
What about Shuisheng?

78
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:28,720
How is he?

79
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:29,360
Is he...

80
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,079
Shuisheng is still alive.

81
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,319
He's just taken quite a beating.

82
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:34,959
Qiuying, don't cry.

83
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:35,639
He's taken quite a beating...

84
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,360
You two grown men,

85
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,759
hurry up and think of something!

86
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,800
Qiuying,

87
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,519
what exactly happened to you last night?

88
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,240
Did you really see ghost soldiers?

89
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,839
I don't remember anything from last night.

90
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,920
When I woke up this morning,

91
00:05:48,519 --> 00:05:50,120
I found myself under the bed.

92
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:50,680
Right,

93
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:51,920
I'm the one who hid you there.

94
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,759
What ghost soldiers?

95
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,360
Master,

96
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,839
the ghost soldiers that hag Liu summoned.

97
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,240
She said you summoned lower-altar soldiers,

98
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,600
while hers were upper-altar soldiers,

99
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,680
a hundred times stronger than yours.

100
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:03,720
So did you actually see the ghost soldiers?

101
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,040
I was too far away to see clearly.

102
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:08,279
But I saw on top of Qingfeng Stronghold,

103
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,040
five-colored smoke signals rising.

104
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,600
That's called soul-binding smoke.

105
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,560
Upper-altar soldiers, my foot.

106
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,079
As if Liu Kanshui is capable of that.

107
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,040
So you mean,

108
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,519
we walked right into an ambush.

109
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,959
So what do we do now?

110
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,519
Save him, of course!

111
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,720
If all else fails, I'll find Xiaolian.

112
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,680
The two of us can coordinate from inside and out.

113
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,399
Don't get yourself captured

114
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:36,959
along with him.

115
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,519
Fine.

116
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,040
That Li Chuanzhong...

117
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,279
For him to become Brigade Commander,

118
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,519
he must have his own tricks.

119
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,079
Right now, he's fishing,

120
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,399
just waiting for you to take the bait.

121
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,600
Brigade Commander,

122
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,079
as they say, speed is vital in warfare.

123
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:49,240
Why not get Shuisheng's confession fast

124
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,839
and wipe out the Communist bandits soon?

125
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,120
Lady Immortal,

126
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:57,680
your powers may be unfathomable,

127
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,680
but when it comes to warfare,

128
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,600
you're an amateur.

129
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:05,920
These guerrillas may be few in number,

130
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,639
with shabby weapons,

131
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:08,680
but,

132
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,800
they appear and vanish like ghosts.

133
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:12,879
When you look for them,

134
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:15,040
they vanish without a trace.

135
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,639
When they strike,

136
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:20,160
they drop from the sky without warning.

137
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,040
So,

138
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:27,399
you're using Shuisheng as bait.

139
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:31,680
It all depends on whether this bait

140
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,639
works or not.

141
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:35,319
So, Master,

142
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,480
what do we do?

143
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,279
Master,

144
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,920
I beg you, please save Shuisheng!

145
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:42,399
Both of us will slave away to repay you!

146
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:43,439
I'm begging you!

147
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,519
No, no, no.

148
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,399
Get up, get up.

149
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,720
Master!

150
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,319
Master!

151
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:48,839
Get up.

152
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:50,480
Master!

153
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:50,920
Qiuying,

154
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:52,920
don't worry.

155
00:07:54,439 --> 00:07:56,160
I've already come up with a plan.

156
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,279
You have?

157
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,439
Old Sun, hurry up, Old Sun!

158
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,040
Time to go home.

159
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,279
Go home.

160
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,639
Let's go. What's wrong?

161
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:15,920
Old Sun.

162
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,480
Why didn't we see this this morning?

163
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:20,639
Right.

164
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,720
This must've appeared just today.

165
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:25,519
Come on.

166
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,199
Let's see which deity it is.

167
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,160
Okay, okay, let's look.

168
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,519
The Fox Goddess!

169
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,679
The Fox Goddess!

170
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,320
Yes, yes, yes.

171
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,039
I heard it's the mayor's daughter.

172
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,679
Qiuying became a deity after she died.

173
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:46,679
Fox Goddess, Fox Goddess.

174
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:47,960
Greetings, Fox Goddess.

175
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:48,919
Fox Goddess.

176
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:50,519
You two, do not be afraid.

177
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,600
Who?

178
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,399
Who?

179
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,559
Who's there?

180
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:58,399
I'm the Fox Goddess who grants all wishes.

181
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,320
Fox Goddess!

182
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,519
Fox Goddess!

183
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:03,240
Whatever wishes you have,

184
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,159
you may speak them out.

185
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:07,399
Fox Goddess,

186
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,960
my son is getting married,

187
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,919
but we're still short two silver dollars.

188
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:12,919
Please, Fox Goddess, help us.

189
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:13,519
Fox Goddess,

190
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,120
please help us.

191
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,080
Help us, Fox Goddess.

192
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,840
It's real, it's real, it's real!

193
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:25,480
Thank you, Fox Goddess!

194
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,840
Oh, Goddess, Goddess

195
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:37,679
I like the Zhang family's wife

196
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,879
Could you help us be together?

197
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,320
You lecher!

198
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:47,399
If you ever harbor such thoughts again,

199
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:49,440
don't blame me for being merciless.

200
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,679
I won't, I won't!

201
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,639
I'll never dare again!

202
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,440
Have you heard?

203
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,200
Up on Wild Fox Ridge,

204
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,240
a Fox Goddess shrine suddenly appeared.

205
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,600
And they say she's incredibly powerful.

206
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:07,960
Really?

207
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:11,000
Is the Fox Goddess really that powerful?

208
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,440
She is!

209
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,360
Incredibly powerful!

210
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,320
About my wife's illness,

211
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,559
I told the Fox Goddess,

212
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:18,399
and she gave me a prescription.

213
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,519
My wife took it and recovered.

214
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:22,159
Are you serious?

215
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,799
Whether you believe it or not,

216
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:24,679
go try it yourself.

217
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,240
Alright.

218
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:25,840
Let's go try it.

219
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,200
Let's go!

220
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,519
What's the rush?

221
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,440
Go at night.

222
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,879
That's the only way to see the Fox Goddess.

223
00:10:30,879 --> 00:10:31,519
What?

224
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:32,440
At night?

225
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,519
At night?

226
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,919
So the Fox Goddess likes to sleep in?

227
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:38,200
Don't talk nonsense.

228
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:41,080
The Fox Goddess has quite a temper.

229
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:44,000
If what you ask for is wicked,

230
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,440
she'll devour you on the spot.

231
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:47,919
This...

232
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,879
Sis.

233
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,679
Last time, the Fox Goddess nearly ate me.

234
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,440
No way I'm going this time.

235
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:56,279
If Qiuying really became the Fox Goddess,

236
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,960
I'll go talk to her.

237
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:00,159
Even if she's become a goddess,

238
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,879
we're still family.

239
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:03,679
Sis...

240
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,440
Don't you get it?

241
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,399
Don't talk about family.

242
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,840
If it weren't for our family,

243
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,200
Qiuying wouldn't have died.

244
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,759
Qiuying...

245
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,720
Mom's the one who failed you.

246
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:25,799
Sis.

247
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,759
Alright, stop crying.

248
00:11:27,759 --> 00:11:28,320
I promise you,

249
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,639
I promise I'll go with you, okay?

250
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,159
Stop crying.

251
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,679
The Fox Goddess is so powerful.

252
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,399
She really is.

253
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:44,279
She told me to dig up two herbs and eat them.

254
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,960
My stomachache went away immediately.

255
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,519
You two have seen the Fox Goddess?

256
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,120
What does she look like?

257
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,759
With our mortal eyes,

258
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,519
how could we ever see her true form?

259
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,159
It's the clay statue that speaks.

260
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:56,960
That's right.

261
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:57,840
Impossible.

262
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,799
But I clearly saw her that day.

263
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:01,639
You must've been drunk.

264
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:03,360
You think the Goddess is your relative?

265
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,879
The Goddess IS my relative.

266
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,679
Still hungover, are you?

267
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:07,559
Let's go.

268
00:12:08,879 --> 00:12:09,679
What a joker.

269
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:12,519
The Goddess wouldn't let us see her.

270
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:13,080
Right.

271
00:12:13,879 --> 00:12:14,480
Let's hurry along.

272
00:12:21,039 --> 00:12:22,279
Why are there so many people?

273
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,559
When will it ever be our turn?

274
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:24,879
Sis.

275
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,679
Come with me.

276
00:12:30,919 --> 00:12:31,759
Hey, what are you doing?

277
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:33,480
Get to the back of the line.

278
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,000
Why should I line up?

279
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:35,679
Everyone lines up.

280
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:36,639
Why aren't you lining up?

281
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:37,559
Yeah!

282
00:12:37,559 --> 00:12:39,000
The Fox Goddess is my niece.

283
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:42,000
I'm just family coming to pay respects.

284
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:42,759
Why should I line up?

285
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:45,080
The Fox Goddess is your niece?

286
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,960
And I'm your great uncle!

287
00:12:48,519 --> 00:12:49,840
Let them through.

288
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,000
Did you hear?

289
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,159
Sis.

290
00:12:53,519 --> 00:12:53,919
Let's go.

291
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:04,679
Qiuying...

292
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,240
All of this...

293
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:08,840
is the food you loved when you were alive.

294
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,559
Mother...

295
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:11,840
bought it all for you.

296
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,679
You're not my mother.

297
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:15,720
You're an accomplice in my murder.

298
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:17,919
We're done for.

299
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,279
The Fox Goddess is about to get angry.

300
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:22,120
Sis, hurry and go!

301
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,399
I'm not leaving.

302
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,080
My daughter...

303
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:28,519
After you left,

304
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:31,120
Mother didn't want to live anymore.

305
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,039
If Mother dies,

306
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:35,080
will you be able to forgive me?

307
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,759
Then Mother...

308
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,840
will die right here for you to see.

309
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,200
Sis!

310
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:41,639
So be it.

311
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,879
I now rank among the immortals.

312
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:46,639
I won't stoop to a mortal's level.

313
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:49,000
If you truly want to repent,

314
00:13:49,639 --> 00:13:51,080
then set Shuisheng free.

315
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:52,960
Yes.

316
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,120
I'll see to it right away.

317
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,759
Come on out.

318
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,480
The crowd's all gone now.

319
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,320
Let's take a break too.

320
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:06,799
Come out.

321
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:11,039
Let's go.

322
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,240
Auntie Xiaoling,

323
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,559
I didn't know you're so good with puppets,

324
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,080
and your ventriloquism was this good too.

325
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,759
Qiuying,

326
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:18,679
you don't know,

327
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:19,919
your Auntie Xiaoling

328
00:14:20,159 --> 00:14:22,639
used to be the star performer

329
00:14:23,399 --> 00:14:24,240
of all of Yinyang Ferry.

330
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,919
Star or no star,

331
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,639
folks who roam the world

332
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:32,639
always need a few tricks up their sleeves.

333
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:37,120
Goddess, please eat first.

334
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:37,960
Goddess, please eat first.

335
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:40,279
So you're the ones pulling these tricks.
